==English==

===Etymology===
Refers to [[w:Julius Caesar|Caesar's]] crossing of the [[w:Rubicon|Rubicon]] to [[wage]] [[civil war]] with [[w:Rome|Rome.]]

===Verb===
'''to [[cross]] the [[Rubicon]]'''
# {{idiom}} To make an [[irreversible]] [[decision]].

